    AdminModules --> Logout
    UserModules --> Logout
    
    Logout -->|Yes| ClearSession[Clear Session Data]
    Logout -->|No| SuperAdminModules
    Logout -->|No| AdminModules
    Logout -->|No| UserModules
    
